      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride that gets the job done? This car is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has some wear and mechanical issues that will need attention, so it's a great fit for a handy buyer or someone looking for a budget-friendly project vehicle. It does run and can be driven, but we want to be upfront: this one needs some TLC to shine again. If you're mechanically inclined or just need basic transportation on a tight budget, this could be the opportunity you've been waiting for!",
