    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is priced accordingly \u2014 we want to be completely upfront with potential buyers. The car has significant mechanical issues that will require substantial repair work before it can be considered reliably drivable. The exterior shows considerable wear including multiple dents, scratches, and paint damage beyond typical aging. The interior is worn and shows heavy use. This vehicle is best suited for a mechanically experienced buyer, someone looking for a project car, or a buyer who intends to use it for parts. It is not recommended for someone seeking a daily driver without first investing in serious repairs. What you see is what you get, and we encourage an in-person inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 7500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and represents a solid, reliable option for a buyer looking for dependable everyday transportation. The exterior shows only minor wear consistent with normal use \u2014 small surface scratches here and there, but no significant dents or rust. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with seats and trim in good shape and all major controls functioning properly. The engine runs smoothly and the car has been regularly serviced; mechanically, it's in strong shape. Tires have good tread remaining, and the brakes are in solid working order. This is an honest, well-kept vehicle that has been cared for \u2014 not perfect, but genuinely good and ready to drive daily without concern.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the market today. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains its original deep luster, no dents, no scratches, and chrome or trim pieces that shine as if they just left the showroom floor. The interior is equally impressive: seats, carpeting, dashboard, and all surfaces are pristine with no fading, cracking, or wear to speak of. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and electrical \u2014 are in perfect working order. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and shows it in every detail. Serious buyers who demand the best will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Ready to find your next dependable daily driver? This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it's been well cared for and shows only the normal signs of regular use you'd expect. The mechanicals are solid, the interior is clean and comfortable, and it presents nicely overall. A few minor cosmetic scuffs here and there keep it honest, but nothing that takes away from its reliability or appeal. If you're looking for a quality used car at a fair price, this one deserves a serious look!",
